data.description: Single story home located on corner lot in South Merced.  Walking distance to local school.  this home features 4 bedrooms / 2 full bathrooms and an attached 2 car garage.  Interior feature fresh paint throughout and newer carpet and luxury vinyl plank flooring plus an indoor laundry room.  Corner lot and good-sized backyard.  Great room concept, kitchen is U-Shaped and features an eat in area / dining area with sliding door to the backyard.  Come take a look today to see if this home is right for you!
